OL,6,FA member of a South Shields crime gang
OL,7,Fthat tortured three men inside a
OL,8,Fgarage has been jailed for more than
OL,9,F10 years.
OL,11,FCraig Seales was part of a gang that
OL,12,Flured victims to a lock-up he owned
OL,13,Fand held them prisoners on 18
OL,14,FSeptember 2023.
OL,16,FThey demanded significant amounts of
OL,17,Fmoney from the victims and their
OL,18,Ffamilies to secure their release
OL,19,Ffollowing a dispute over drugs.
