OL,6,FSeales, of Rembrandt Avenue, South
OL,7,FShields was sentenced during a hearing
OL,8,Fat the same court on Monday 16
OL,9,FSeptember.
OL,11,FGlenn Gatland, mitigating, had told
OL,12,Fthe court Seales facilitated what
OL,13,Foccurred but was not aware of what was
OL,14,Fgoing to take place. He added he was
OL,15,Fnot involved in supplying cocaine or
OL,16,Fany drugs the gang were involved in
OL,17,Fpeddling.
