OL,6,FProsecutor Richard Wright KC said the
OL,7,Fgang's victims were subjected to
OL,8,Fviolence including punches and kicks.
OL,9,FA shovel and a blow torch were also
OL,10,Fused, while corrosive substances were
OL,11,Fpoured on them.
OL,13,FThe court heard one of the victims
OL,14,Ftried to convince the group he had
OL,15,Fmoney at home and could get it, but
OL,16,Fthe defendants refused to let him
OL,17,Fleave.
