OL,4,Ctorture of men in garage
OL,6,FSentencing Seales, Judge Amanda Rippon
OL,7,Fsaid the three victims were "abused
OL,8,Fand tortured" inside a garage by the
OL,9,Fgang.
OL,11,FOne of the victims was said to have
OL,12,Ffelt "helpless" and that those
OL,13,Finvolved "terrified me". In a
OL,14,Fstatement, he said he thought he was
OL,15,Fgoing to die during the ordeal and
OL,16,Fthat he said a Muslim prayer in his
OL,17,Fhead which is usually recited before
OL,18,Fdeath.
