OL,4,Ctorture of men in garage
OL,6,FThe victim, who was eventually
OL,7,Freleased, went on to flee the North
OL,8,FEast with his family.
OL,10,FJudge Rippon said there was "no
OL,11,Fjustification" for the injuries the
OL,12,Fvictims sustained and that each
OL,13,Fdefendant was "culpable for the next".
OL,14,FShe added some played "discernible
OL,15,Fparts" with Seales providing the "all
OL,16,Fimportant premises".
OL,18,FShe sentenced Seales to 10 years and
OL,19,Ffour months in prison. A restraining
OL,20,Forder was also imposed and will last
OL,21,Funtil further order.
